    "body": "Hi @Monali109, thank you for your report! As I can see from screenshot this is expected behavior for the application. To recover an account which was created before you need to use your secret phrase that was generated along with your account you are trying to restore. \r\nPlease keep in mind the pass phrase should be exactly the same otherwise new account will be created instead. We also have an open issue https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/1228 that would not allow to proceed with recover untill the `Passphrase` field is populated correctly and https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/1224 that will add password length checking functionality.\r\n I hope the flow will be less confusing soon! :) \r\n\r\n",
